org.stormgears.WebDashboard.GameControl

Class GameControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stormgears.WebDashboard.GameControl.GameControl
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Checkboxes, Progress, Radios, Select, Slider, Spacer, Text, TextArea, TextField

    public abstract class GameControl
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class with fields for most game controls. An array of GameControls can be added to the dashboard using WebDashboard.set("config.controls", new GameControl[]{...});

    • Field Detail

      • label

        public final java.lang.String label
        Text to be displayed near the control.

      • path

        public final java.lang.String path
        Specifies what JSON path the control is bound to. The control will display the value of the JSON path in WebDashboard's distributed hashtable, and changes made to the control's value will be propagated to the hashtable.

      • width

        public int width
        The width of the control, ranging from 1 to 12.

        WebDashboard displays controls in a twelve-column grid. Controls are added to this grid, with the specified width. When the width in a single row exceeds the 12 column grid width, the control will wrap to the next line.

      • large

        public boolean large
        Specifies whether the control is displayed with large text.

        Specifies whether the user is allowed to make modifications to the control's value.
